# Installation

## Prerequisites

- Node.js 18+ (or Bun 1.0+)
- Git

## Quick Install

=== "npm"

    ```bash
    npm install {{name}}
    ```

=== "pnpm"

    ```bash
    pnpm add {{name}}
    ```

=== "bun"

    ```bash
    bun add {{name}}
    ```

## From Source

```bash
git clone https://github.com/{{author}}/{{name}}.git
cd {{name}}
{{#if useBun}}
bun install
{{else}}
npm install
{{/if}}
```

## Verify Installation

```bash
{{#if useBun}}
bun run --version
{{else}}
npm run --version
{{/if}}
```

